Fluentis Live Update is the application to proceed with fluentis suite **installation**, **updates**, and **porting** of customizations.  
Fluentis Live Update, consists of a webApplication, a dedicated database on a SQL Server instance and also a service to be installed on the server which is called ***Fluentis Installer Service***.

:::danger
***FluentisInstaller* must be installed on each servers** involved in the Fluentis installion process (i.e. all the servers that host SQL Server installations or fluentis apps installations) **and properly registered** inside the  **FluentisLiveUpdate** web app, under **Installer Services** page. 
:::